    GetDataFciRespPars

    public static class GetDataFciRespPars.StartupInformation
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class StartupInformation. The Calypso applications return the Startup Information in the answer to the Select Application command. The Startup Information contains several data fields (applicationType,software issuer...)
